{"tid":2140181,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtube對家整左條咁既片","createTime":"2020-08-04T22:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T04:00:26.000Z","uid":43196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a0aaceaa281322a34111ae8f1b3f0e33c65f79dd","tid":2140181,"uid":43196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:12:30.000Z","msg":"睇睇下片，彈條廣告出黎<br />\n通常彈都係Netflix 同game既廣告<br />\n但佢彈條兩分既鐘既片出黎，內容係影射場運動<br />\n影射各大學同埋用黑社會化左參與運動既人<br />\n我好奇之下睇曬條片，真係好撚嘔心<br />\n繼續按入去，條片係三日前先有<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以令條片收皮<br />\n<br />\n呢啲咁單一方向既訊息又唔係産品，點解可以變左廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條link係到，唔想幫佢加view數<br />\n所以加密左幾次，要按幾下先入到去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8306ab04eb0c73e3263bd16c64794a60ecc8c775","tid":2140181,"uid":43196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:13:24.000Z","msg":"唔知開乜台<br />\n<br />\n所以開左係創意<br />\n有錯勿屌"},{"pid":"37db59d60ea4b3544a13be99776a9a46738d001d","tid":2140181,"uid":43196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:14:18.000Z","msg":"推到條片收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db725d251a1d1646d3390900f46d4d5fa0e151d5","tid":2140181,"uid":43196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64067685365356483e40d4e06689ae52fb44ebf","tid":2140181,"uid":43196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce24e1cc6cfb14ecd8af4a3aa95846228f87de7","tid":2140181,"uid":43196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:16:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推，一齊report條片"},{"pid":"080db268047429fec2603e935158d8c73a537ee6","tid":2140181,"uid":43196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply